[06/12/2017 19:16:33] <font color="#ffffff">Bienvenida.</font>
[06/12/2017 19:16:35] <font color="#ffffff">Qué bonita. Hola.</font>
[06/12/2017 19:16:35] <font color="#ffffff">Hola.</font>
